{
  "id": "ch3_lyanna",
  "slides": [
    {
      "text": "塔室昏暗，\n玫瑰的香气已经败了，\n只剩下血和蜡烛的气味。",
      "subtext": "",
      "duration": 5.5,
	  "scene_art": "lyanna_chamber",
	  "camera_style": "candle_breath"
    },
    {
      "text": "「奈德……」",
      "subtext": "那声音很低，\n低到他几乎以为是自己的幻觉。\n但他听到了。",
      "duration": 6.0,
	  "scene_art": "lyanna_chamber",
	  "camera_style": "candle_breath"
    },
    {
      "text": "「答应我，奈德……\n答应我……」",
      "subtext": "他跪下去，握住那双手。\n「我答应你。」\n他说。\n「我答应你。」",
      "duration": 7.0,
	  "scene_art": "lyanna_chamber",
	  "camera_style": "candle_breath"
    },
    {
      "text": "婴儿的哭声，\n从某处传来。",
      "subtext": "——黑屏。",
      "duration": 5.0,
	  "scene_art": "lyanna_chamber",
	  "camera_style": "candle_breath"
    }
  ]
}
